{"tid":736414,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦教練高普引用球隊座右銘「你永遠不會獨行」，鼓勵受困洞穴的少年","createTime":"2018-07-10T08:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T10:47:00.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81348ebf0b4f2f4dfa94d7d88932e97cf6c1c3c3","tid":736414,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"這支名叫「野豬」的少年足球隊12名隊員年齡介於11到16歲，25歲的教練6月23日在訓練活動後帶領他們到地下洞穴探險，因大雨積水而受困。<br />\n<br />\n英國利物浦足球隊（Liverpool）教練高普（Jurgen Klopp）引用球隊座右銘「你永遠不會獨行」（You'll never walk alone），鼓勵受困洞穴的少年。泰國有很多人關注英格蘭足球超級聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n在送到CNN的影片中，高普說：「要堅強，我們與你們同在。我們正關注所有新聞，每刻都希望你們能重見天日，我們對此都非常樂觀，希望能在數分鐘、數小時或數天後發生。」"},{"pid":"f5a247856530e016191521a2aab5f4291634d8e6","tid":736414,"uid":42409,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"死利狗又搞事"},{"pid":"a68be22ae7ea0af56ab62d56ef94eb402616edaa","tid":736414,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a247856530e016191521a2aab5f4291634d8e6","tid":736414,"uid":42409,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"死利狗又搞事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"放暑假得閒出去玩下啦"},{"pid":"4907d6f4a1d9443d6948c1993030324fb63e620c","tid":736414,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95538bf50158e0ca075d5ebd7006c66160934de7","tid":736414,"uid":63414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:52:15.000Z","msg":"You'll never walk again"},{"pid":"f020b60e53846449f7a44d65fbfb838ea2ea2e6f","tid":736414,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"How about Karius <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca4f866deb24c1916dff0163f0e3a41242a7432","tid":736414,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"同朋友一齊被困"},{"pid":"